    <para id="id1163963099967"><emphasis effect="bold">DIRECTIONS:Â </emphasis>Please respond to the following questions with complete sentences. Be sure to make your answers as detailed as possible, and to check your work for spelling/grammatical errors.</para>
    <para id="id1163984015066">1. Briefly outline the plot/events in your scene.</para>
    <para id="id1163963760835">2. What will be the setting of your scene? How will this setting be effective in enhancing the story?</para>
    <para id="id1163974248197">3. Briefly describe the characters that will appear in your scene (appearance, age, mannerisms, personality, motivations, etc.)</para>
    <para id="id1163962041956">4. How will you start your scene? How will this "hook" your audience?</para>
    <para id="id1654088">5. How will you make your scene stand out? What will be unique and/or creative about it?</para>
